Twin Peaks Community College
Twin Peaks Community College was the community college in Twin Peaks.
Norma Jennings graduated from Twin Peaks Community College, earning a degree in Home Economics.
Audrey Horne attended the college, obtaining a degree in Economics and Business Administration.
